videos.title: #1168 - CHI Health Center in Omaha, NE
videos.overview: On a highly-explosive SmackDown, Universal Champion Roman Reigns came face-to-face with his former brother-in-arms turned Royal Rumble challenger Seth Rollins, Aliyah broke a WWE record against Natalya, new challengers to the SmackDown Tag Team Title emerged and Lita delivered a Twist of Fate to SmackDown Women's Champion Charlotte Flair.

videos.title: #1171 - Paycom Center in Oklahoma City, OK
videos.overview: After winning the Royal Rumble Match, Ronda Rousey came to SmackDown for the first time and declared that she will challenge Charlotte Flair for the SmackDown Women's Title on The Grandest Stage of the Them All. Plus, Goldberg emerged to inform Universal Champion Roman Reigns that he's next at WWE Elimination Chamber.

videos.title: #1172 - Smoothie King Center in New Orleans, LA
videos.overview: Though WWE Official Sonya Deville was ordered to not lay a hand of Naomi, SmackDown Women's Champion Charlotte Flair emerged victorious over The Glow in a hard-fought title match. After the bell, The Baddest Women on the Planet emerged to stop a 2-on-1 onslaught by Flair and Deville.

videos.title: #1173 - Smoothie King Center in New Orleans, LA

videos.title: #1174 - Giant Center in Hershey, PA
videos.overview: On a chaotic SmackDown, WWE Champion Brock Lesnar turned his contract signing with Universal Champion Roman Reigns for the Winner Take All Championship Unification Match completely upside down. Plus, Ronda Rousey repelled an attack by WWE Official Sonya Deville and SmackDown Women's Champion Charlotte Flair and so much more.

videos.title: #1175 - FTX Arena in Miami, FL
videos.overview: Ronda Rousey made Sonya Deville tap out in her SmackDown in-ring debut and introduced SmackDown Women's Champion Charlotte Flair to her excruciating ankle lock. Plus, Johnny Knoxville helped Ricochet capture the Intercontinental Title from Sami Zayn, The Usos conquered The Viking Raiders to retain the SmackDown Tag Team Titles and so much more.

videos.title: #1176 - Legacy Arena in Birmingham, AL
videos.overview: One week after Ronda Rousey surprised SmackDown Women's Champion Charlotte Flair with an ankle lock that made the titleholder tap out, The Opportunity roared back with brutal vengeance on The Baddest Woman on the Planet.

videos.title: #1177 - Spectrum Center in Charlotte, NC

Plus, Charlotte Flair once again got the better of Ronda Rousey after goading her WrestleMania opponent into a fight and planting her through the announce table after Rousey refused to tap out.

videos.title: #1178 - Barclays Center in Brooklyn, NY

Plus, The Usos retained the SmackDown Tag Team Titles against Braun Strowman and Ricochet, Ronda Rousey made her return and so much more.

videos.title: #1353 - Bell Centre in Montreal, QC
videos.overview: John Cena is back on SmackDown after losing the Undisputed WWE Title to Cody Rhodes in a Street Fight at SummerSlam and following the stunning post-match beatdown he received at the hands of Brock Lesnar.WWE Champion Cody Rhodes to address WWE Universe.Alex Shelley and Chris Sabin are back in action after a grueling TLC Match at SummerSlam that saw them fail to capture the WWE Tag Team Title.Their opponents will be Talla Tonga and JC Mateo of The MFTs, and United States Champion Solo Sikoa seems sure to be watching this match closely.

videos.title: #1354 - TD Garden in Boston, MA
videos.overview: Last week, Drew McIntyre Claymore'd Undisputed WWE Champion Cody Rhodes right into the announce table, exploding the side of the table into splinters. This week, The Scottish Warrior will address his heinous actions.Last week, Gargano, Tommaso Ciampa and LeRae confronted The Street Profits, accusing them of hurting LeRae. This week, these two teams will tangle in a grudge match.Now, it's Bliss' turn. Five Feet of Fury is set to step in the ring with the dangerous Piper Niven. The 2025 Andre The Giant Battle Royal Memorial winner is determined to vault himself into the title scene, and The Miz has promised to lead him to those new heights. Fraxiom, meanwhile, are fighting to get back into the WWE Tag Team Title picture as The Wyatt Sicks currently dominate the landscape. Can Melo Don't Miz score a major tag team victory or will Fraxiom be on their way to another championship opportunity?

videos.title: #1355 - 3Arena in Dublin, Ireland
videos.overview: John Cena returns to SmackDown en route to battling Logan Paul at WWE Clash in Paris. Now The Queen is looking for payback when she goes one-on-one with Niven. As a result of a backstage altercation last week, Motor City Machine Guns will take on Melo Don't Miz. After some rough waters in recent weeks, will The Miz and Carmelo Hayes be on the same page against their veteran tandem adversaries?SmackDown's red-hot tag team division continues to set Friday night ablaze as The Street Profits step in the ring with two members of the dangerous MFTs. R-Truth must channel every bit of his inner Ron Killings when he faces the ominous Aleister Black.

videos.title: #1356 - LDLC Arena in Lyon-Décines, France
videos.overview: Sami Zayn has pinned United States Champion Solo Sikoa and continues to be a huge thorn in the side of The MFTs.How will John Cena respond to Logan Paul's blindside attack when he returns to SmackDown just one night before their blockbuster match at WWE Clash in Paris?After fighting through the SmackDown tag teams in recent weeks, The Street Profits and Melo Don't Miz will battle each other for the right to challenge WWE Tag Team Champions Joe Gacy and Dexter Lumis of The Wyatt Sicks. Charlotte Flair and Alexa Bliss are set to defend the WWE Women's Tag Team Championship against Piper Niven and Alba Fyre.  Michin wants a WWE Women's United States Championship Match against Giulia.

videos.title: #1357 - Allstate Arena in Chicago, IL
videos.overview: John Cena is rolling into The Windy City one last time.  After conquering Solo Sikoa last week to finally claim the United States Championship, Sami Zayn returns to SmackDown with the star-spangled title.

videos.title: #1358 - Scope Arena in Norfolk, VA

videos.title: #1359 - Huntington Center in Toledo, OH
videos.overview: The American Nightmare and The Scottish Psychopath will sign the contract for Wrestlepalooza. Brock Lesnar returns to SmackDown and gives an exclusive interview ahead of his blockbuster match with John Cena at Wrestlepalooza.Charlotte Flair and Alexa Bliss will put their title on the line against Chelsea Green and Alba Fyre.For the third week in a row, Sami Zayn will hold a United States Championship Open Challenge on SmackDown. Not one to wait, Carmelo Hayes has already declared that he will be accepting the title opportunity.

videos.title: #1360 - Kia Center in Orlando, FL
videos.overview: WWE Women's Champion Tiffany Stratton is undefeated in 2025. Following a chaotic few weeks, however, the titleholder must now defend the championship against Jade Cargill and Nia Jax in a Triple Threat Match.Cody Rhodes returns to SmackDown with his sights set on World Heavyweight Champion Seth Rollins and the Crown Jewel Title.Sami Zayn will issue his fourth United States Championship Open Challenge in as many weeks. Following recent turmoil, Michin and B-Fab are set to join forces against Women's United States Champion Giulia and Kiana James.

videos.title: #1361 - Heritage Bank Center in Cincinnati, OH
videos.overview: American Nightmare will join forces with The Viper against The Vision.Sami Zayn will issue his fifth United States Championship Open Challenge in as many weeks. WWE Women's Champion Tiffany Stratton sets her sights on Women's World Champion Stephanie Vaquer and the Crown Jewel Championship.

videos.title: #1362 - RAC Arena in Perth, Australia

Find out who will step into the spotlight to challenge the hardest-working titleholder in the business.

videos.title: #1363 - SAP Center in San Jose, CA
videos.overview: After World Heavyweight Champion Seth Rollins defeated Undisputed WWE Champion Cody Rhodes and won the WWE Crown Jewel Title in controversial fashion, Rhodes returns to SmackDown to kick off the show.Jacob Fatu and Drew McIntyre have been engaged in a volatile rivalry, and the aggressive Superstars will finally collide one-on-one. WWE Women's Tag Team Champions Charlotte Flair and Alexa Bliss may not be best friends, but the titleholders have been effective together in the ring.  After stepping up to The Queen and Five Feet of Fury backstage, NXT's Sol Ruca and Zaria are now looking to prove themselves by becoming champions.

videos.title: #1365 - Delta Center in Salt Lake City, UT
videos.overview: What is in store for Undisputed WWE Champion Cody Rhodes and Drew McIntyre when they take part in a Contract Signing just one night before their title rematch at Saturday Night's Main Event?Jade Cargill will address the WWE Universe before battling the titleholder at Saturday Night's Main Event. WWE Women's Tag Team Champion Alexa Bliss is set to clash with her one-time friend Nia Jax. Hayes' new focus did not prevent him from taking exception when Kit Wilson accused him of giving off "toxic masculinity" backstage. Who will be the next Superstar to answer the call?Nia Jax will face WWE Women's Tag Team Champion Charlotte Flair after losing to Alexa Bliss last week. Can Jax fare better against Flair? Can Fenix fell the tree-like Tonga?
